.Im MicroEmacs command
.so me.tni
.TH alarm 3
.XI alarm - "Set an alarm"
.SH NAME
alarm \- Set an alarm
.Me $a
.SH SYNOPSIS
.na
\fBalarm\fR
"\fImessage\fR" "\fIhours\fR" "\fIminutes\fR"
.ad
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B alarm
creates an alarm notification which displays  "\fImessage\fR" to the user. The
alarm  time  is   specified   as  an  elapsed   time  in   "\fIhours\fR"   and
"\fIminutes\fR" from the time of creation.
.PP
The message is printed on the screen using
.Ht osd 2 .
.SH NOTES
.B alarm
is a macro defined in \fCosdmisc.emf\fR.
.SH "SEE ALSO"
.na
.Ht osd 2 .
.ad
.FH
